---
import { DONATION } from 'astrowind:config';
import Content from '~/components/common/Content.astro';
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Button from '~/components/common/Button.astro';
import CopyText from '~/components/common/CopyText.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Donation ‚Äî Supporting the Project',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: false,
};

const breadCrumbLinks = [
  { text: 'Home', href: '/' },
  { text: 'Donation', href: '/donate' },
];

const cryptoLink = DONATION['cryptoPaymentLink'] || 'https://www.example.com/crypto-donate';
const bankLink = DONATION['bankCardPaymentLink'] || 'https://www.example.com/bank-card-donate';
---

<PageLayout
  {breadCrumbLinks}
  {metadata}
  heroItems={[
    {
      title: 'Supporting the Project',
      bgImage: '~/assets/images/pages/donation.webp',
    },
  ]}
>
  <Content>
    <h1>Supporting the ‚ÄúBusiness Pathfinder Chronicles‚Äù Project</h1>
    <h2>Author‚Äôs Gratitude</h2>
    <p>
      Dear Friend,<br />
      Thank you very much for valuing my work, materials, and the time spent developing the ‚ÄúBusiness Pathfinder
      Chronicles‚Äù project. Your willingness to support the project is the best reward for me, Sergey V. P.
      Your financial assistance is not merely a donation; it is a direct investment in the creation of new,
      high-quality, and in-depth content.
    </p>

    <h2>üõë Important Legal Notice</h2>
    <p>
      Your payment made on this page constitutes a
      <strong>voluntary, gratuitous donation (gift)</strong> in favor of the Site Administration
      (Sergey V. P.) for the development of the project.
    </p>
    <p>
      By making a payment, you confirm that this donation is not payment for any product, service, or other
      reciprocal equivalent. In accordance with the <strong>Public Offer Agreement</strong> (Section 7),
      the donation is <strong>non-refundable</strong>, except in cases of technical error by the payment system.
      By transferring funds, you confirm that your intent to donate is voluntary and informed.
    </p>

    <h2>How to Make a Donation</h2>
    <p>
      We value your anonymity and security, which is why the preferred method of support is payment via cryptocurrency.
    </p>

    <h3>1. Cryptocurrency (Preferred Method)</h3>
    <table class="table-auto border-collapse border border-gray-400 mt-4 mb-6">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-gray-100">
          <th class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">Currency</th>
          <th class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">Network</th>
          <th class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">Wallet Address (Public Key)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">USDT</td>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">TRC-20 (Tron)</td>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">
            <CopyText text={DONATION['usdtTrc20Address']} />
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">USDT</td>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">ERC-20 (Ethereum)</td>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">
            <CopyText text={DONATION['usdtErc20Address']} />
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">USDC</td>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">Solana</td>
          <td class="border border-gray-400 px-4 py-2">
            <CopyText text={DONATION['usdcSolAddress']} />
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>Donation Instructions</h4>
    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mb-6">
      <li>Copy the corresponding wallet address listed above.</li>
      <li>Open your cryptocurrency wallet or exchange account.</li>
      <li>Ensure you have selected the correct network.</li>
      <li>Specify the amount and confirm the transaction.</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>2. Traditional Methods (PayPal / Other)</h3>
    <p>If you prefer to use traditional payment methods, please use the link below.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-4">
      <Button href={bankLink} text="Pay by Bank Card" target="_blank" variant="primary" type="link" />
      <Button href={cryptoLink} text="Pay with Cryptocurrency" target="_blank" variant="primary" type="link" />
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8">
      Once again, thank you very much for your support! Your contribution helps the ‚ÄúBusiness Pathfinder Chronicles‚Äù
      grow and share unique experience with thousands of readers.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 font-semibold">
      Sincerely,<br />Sergey V. P.<br />Author and Administrator of the Project
    </p>
  </Content>
</PageLayout>
